<div id="main-b-visual">
  <div class="containser pt-5">
    <h4 class="title ml-4 mb-5"><i class="fas fa-baby fa-3x"></i> <%= @user.name %>さんの詳細データ</h4>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-xs-6 user-data mx-auto my-5">
        <table class="table table-bordered table-color ml-2">
          <tr>
            <th class="table-active font-large">身長</th>
            <td class="font-large text-center"><%= @user.height %><span> cm</span></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th class="table-active font-large">体重</th>
            <td class="font-large text-center"><%= @user.weight %><span> kg</span></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th class="table-active font-large">BMI</th>
            <td class="font-large text-center"><%= @user.bmi %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th class="table-active font-large">体型</th>
            <td class="font-large text-center"><%= render "users/style",user: @user %></td>
          </tr>
        </table>
        <p class="style-p">
          ※ 体型の基準は、BMI値が<br>18未満　⇨　『やせ型』<br>18以上25未満　⇨　『標準型』<br>25以上　⇨　『肥満型』
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-xs-12 back d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center my-4">
        <%= link_to "戻る", user_path(@user),class:"back-link " %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
